name: JPUtils
author: JPMB2017 & TR0LPlays
description:
A few QOL features to improve the gameplay.
/aw to enable auto-warp for both Normal and Master-Mode (No Kuudra cuz dt to open chest).
/fb to disable FallingBlocks.
/fishingutils to disable.
/vanq to disable Vanquisher Alert.
/golempq to disable Auto-PQ toggle.
/kft to enable Kuudra Features.
/autosb to toggle auto-rejoin SkyBlock.
